== [http://love2d.org LÖVE] ==
[[File:Love_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|200px]]

LÖVE is a framework you can use to make 2D games in Lua and also allows for commercial use. It features a [http://www.love2d.org/wiki/Category:Games lot of games] including [http://stabyourself.net Stabyourself games] such as {{Package|games-arcade/mari0}}, {{Package|games-arcade/notpacman}} or {{Package|games-arcade/trosh}}. It is slotted in portage to avoid compatibility problems with old games, slot "0" being always the latest release.

